discussion.content:
Complete question: https://vceguide.com/which-three-actions-should-you-perform-in-sequence-576/

The answer should be: 
1) Create RG, and then deploy a web app to the RG;
2) From the Automation script blade of the RG, click "Add to Library";
3) From the Templates service, select the template, and then share the template to the web admins.

The correct answer, in order, is:
1) Create RG, and then deploy a web app to the RG;
2) From the Automation script blade of the RG, click "Add to Library";
3) From the Templates service, select the template, and then share the template to the web admins.
